'''拜鲁尔·克里希那马查尔·桑达拉拉亚·艾扬格'''（{{lang-en|'''Bellur Krishnamachar Sundararaja Iyengar'''，简称 '''B. K. S. Iyengar'''}}，{{bd|1918年|12月14日|2014年|8月20日}}）是一位[[印度|印度]][[瑜伽|瑜伽]]大师，他是[[艾扬格瑜伽|艾扬格瑜伽]]的创始人，被认为是全球最负盛名的一位瑜伽教师<ref name="igengar">Aubrey, Allison. "Light on life: B.K.S. Iyengar's Yoga insights". ''Morning Edition: National Public Radio'', 10 November 1995. [http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=4979052 (full text)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=4979052 |date=20140823024038 }} Accessed 4 July 2007</ref><ref name=gather>{{cite news | last =Stukin | first =Stacie | title =Yogis gather around the guru | newspaper =Los Angeles Times | date =2005-10-10 | url =http://articles.latimes.com/2005/oct/10/health/he-iyengar10 | accessdate =2013-01-09 | archive-date =2012-04-11 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20120411205338/http://articles.latimes.com/2005/oct/10/health/he-iyengar10 | dead-url =no }}</ref>。他出版了包括《[[瑜伽之光|瑜伽之光]]》在内许多瑜伽练习书籍，在世界各地有许多人学习他创立的瑜伽练习课程。他是现代瑜伽之父——[[Tirumalai_Krishnamacharya|Tirumalai Krishnamacharya]]最早的一位学生<ref>{{cite book |last= Iyengar|first= B.K.S. |authorlink= B.K.S. Iyengar |title= Astadala Yogamala |year= 2000 |publisher= Allied Publishers |location= New Delhi, India |isbn= 978-8177640465
|page= 53}}</ref>。他普及了瑜伽，并将之传播到了全世界<ref>{{cite book |last= Sjoman |first= N.E. |title= The Yoga Tradition of the Mysore Palace | edition = 2nd | year= 1999|publisher= Abhinav Publications |location= New Delhi, India|isbn= 81-7017-389-2 |page= 41}}</ref>。他因此被许多人尊称为“尊敬的上师”(guru-ji)<ref name=c22iyengar-obit>{{cite news|title=瑜珈大师艾扬格去世，曾将瑜珈引入西方|url=http://cn.nytimes.com/obits/20140822/c22iyengar-obit/|accessdate=2015-05-14|publisher=纽约时报中文网|date=2014年8月22日|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518105414/http://cn.nytimes.com/obits/20140822/c22iyengar-obit/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1991年艾扬格获得[[印度政府|印度政府]]颁发的[[莲花士勋章|莲花士勋章]]，2002年获得[[莲花装勋章|莲花装勋章]]，2014年获得[[莲花赐勋章|莲花赐勋章]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/padma-vibhushan-for-yoga-guru-iyengar-padma-bhushan-for-paes-gopichand-vidya-balan/article1-1176739.aspx |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-08-22 |archive-date=2014-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140825074257/http://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/padma-vibhushan-for-yoga-guru-iyengar-padma-bhushan-for-paes-gopichand-vidya-balan/article1-1176739.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Padma Awards Announced|publisher=Press Information Bureau, Ministry of Home Affairs|url=http://pib.nic.in/newsite/erelease.aspx?relid=102735|date=2014-01-25|accessdate=2014-01-26|archive-date=2014-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140128220003/http://pib.nic.in/newsite/erelease.aspx?relid=102735|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2004年，艾扬格被《[[时代杂志|时代杂志]]》评选为[[时代百大人物|全球最有影响的一百位名人之一]]<ref>[http://www.time.com/time/subscriber/2004/time100/heroes/100iyengar.html 2004 TIME 100 – B.K.S. Iyengar] {{Wayback|url=http://www.time.com/time/subscriber/2004/time100/heroes/100iyengar.html |date=20101228174009 }} Heroes & Icons, TIME.</ref><ref name="BKS">{{cite web |author=By B.K.S. Iyengar |url=http://www.yogajournal.com/views/1843_1.cfm |title=Yoga News & Trends – Light on Iyengar |publisher=Yoga Journal |accessdate=2012-11-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070831043522/http://www.yogajournal.com/views/1843_1.cfm |archivedate=2007-08-31 }}</ref>。

==生平==
1918年12月14日，艾扬格出生在印度[[卡纳塔克邦|卡纳塔克邦]]一个贫穷家庭里，排行十一。他的父亲是一位教师，在他9岁时死于[[阑尾炎|阑尾炎]]。童年时艾扬格曾患过[[肺结核|肺结核]]、[[伤寒|伤寒]]与[[疟疾|疟疾]]，16岁开始学习瑜伽。<ref name=c22iyengar-obit />

1952年，他与瑜伽爱好者耶胡迪·梅纽因(Yehudi Menuhin)结伴旅行，从事瑜伽的传授<ref name=c22iyengar-obit />。

